com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheapstruct

Interface OffHeapStructCollection

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OffHeapStructArray, OffHeapStructArrayList

    public interface OffHeapStructCollection
    Base interface for off-heap struct (memory areas of equal sizes) collection.
    Author:
    alexkasko Date: 7/3/13
